{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6f184dc67b","title":"大字报——肃反","origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑3》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月25日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a1c095099","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"6f184dc67b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"222c241b8a","name":"成都工学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ee1b74201e","type":"title","text":"大字报——肃反","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6f184dc67b"},{"id":"fe567b78a4","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6f184dc67b"},{"id":"157943c2bb","type":"paragraph","text":"摸风捉雨，大胆怀疑，看管起来，发动群众，反覆斗争，日以继夜，拳打脚踢，扯落头发，还不上算，关进茅屋，度日如年，搜集材料，强迫接受，以寒(塞？)偏差。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6f184dc67b"},{"id":"6021673ac2","type":"paragraph","text":"李绍文说，成绩很大，反革命分子，数十坦白，真是如此，那还了得！夸大成绩，有功有德，这次运动，要彻底坦白，用心何在，活天冤枉！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6f184dc67b"}],"page":{"id":"fe5855faee","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6f184dc67b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}